<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/make" style="color:black;">make</a>; <a href="/dictionary/work" style="color:black;">work</a>; <a href="/dictionary/compose" style="color:black;">compose</a>, write; act, perform</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 7<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 7 strokes: <a href="/character/我" title="wo3: our, us, i, me, my, we">我</a>, <a href="/character/这" title="zhe4: this, the, here">这</a>, <a href="/character/来" title="lai2: come, coming; return, returning">来</a>, <a href="/character/时" title="shi2: time, season; era, age, period">时</a>, <a href="/character/你" title="ni3: you, second person pronoun">你</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/没" title="mei2: not, have not, none; drown, sink">没</a>, <a href="/character/还" title="hai2: still, yet, also, besides">还</a>, <a href="/character/进" title="jin4: advance, make progress, enter">进</a>, <a href="/character/但" title="dan4: only; but, however, yet, still">但</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/人" title="Kangxi radical 9">人</a>&nbsp;9.5</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 1 <br><small>Other HSK 1 characters: <a href="/character/后" title="hou4: queen, empress, sovereign; (simp. for 後) behind, rear, after">后</a>, <a href="/character/里" title="li3: unit of distance; village; lane">里</a>, <a href="/character/年" title="">年</a>, <a href="/character/下" title="xia4: under, underneath, below; down; inferior; bring down">下</a>, <a href="/character/家" title="jia1: house, home, residence; family">家</a>, <a href="/character/那" title="na4: that, that one, those">那</a>, <a href="/character/多" title="duo1: much, many; more than, over">多</a>, <a href="/character/子" title="zi: offspring, child; fruit, seed of; 1st terrestrial branch">子</a>, <a href="/character/么" title="me: interrogative particle; repetition of a tune small; tender">么</a>, <a href="/character/能" title="neng2: to be able; can, permitted to; abilit